{"tid":1528196,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"韓媒：中港Wanna One粉絲上飛機追星　見面後落機退票　全機人要再安檢航班延誤","createTime":"2019-09-01T13:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T01:55:33.000Z","uid":206117,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f40ceca4808467fa51681bc1dec32a1ff9bed897","tid":1528196,"uid":206117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20181217/s00005/1545039502269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20181217%2Fs00005%2F1545039502269&d=3Z9ZeYaQzwHPi2iIp4702OTimN4xbKJd0qqIWjmG9ok%3D&h=c78793e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20181217%2Fs00005%2F1545039502269&h=6f6ce958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20181217/s00005/1545039502269</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國人氣男團「Wanna One」，上周五（14日）來港出席Mnet亞洲音樂大獎頒獎禮（MAMA）香港站後，韓國傳媒報道，3名內地及香港「粉絲」購買機票，登機「追星」後即下機退票，令全機乘客需重新安檢，航班終延誤約一小時。韓媒報道事件時，在標題以「白癡」（idiot）形容涉事3人。<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：【朝鮮風雲】韓軍確認朝鮮邊防哨站拆毀 無法再作軍事用途<br />\n<br />\n《韓國時報》引述「業界消息」報道，涉事3人均為20多歲，其中兩人來自中國內地，一人來自香港，他們購買Wanna One上周六（15日）回韓航班的頭等、商務及經濟客位機票各一。當Wanna One成員登機時，3人無視機艙服務員阻止，走到成員座位與他們見面，然後在所乘的大韓航空客機起飛前數分鐘，要求下機及退票。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，機組人員已告知3人，根據航空法例，若有人在起飛前下機，出於安全考慮，全機乘客都必須重新接受安檢。惟3人仍堅持落機，結果全機約360名乘客都要重新安檢，航班最終延誤約一小時，航空公司除需為涉事3人退款外，還要為航班延誤而賠償。<br />\n<br />\n《韓國時報》並指，大韓航空曾要求香港警方調查3人，但警方以機上無人報稱有財物或損失為由拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n《北京青年報》報道，涉事航班為上周六下午從香港飛往首爾的KE614航班。報道引述大韓航空的公關公司指，該班機上的確有乘客「因自身原因」申請下機，並完成退票。航班因此延遲約一小時起飛，航空公司需向香港國際機場支付手續費。"},{"pid":"c5e16f16d616ddc915032d7eb1505bd0f12dfe17","tid":1528196,"uid":259345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"我地需要你關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上熱門］［92 &amp; 93］中學生為我地上前線 我地一齊聲援中學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1527952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1527952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0VUpjiC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0VUpjiC.jpg&h=9cea0167&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"048742a112ee8cd29770ba1264d055641e31fa47","tid":1528196,"uid":268927,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:13:35.000Z","msg":"香港真係有好多韓粉，8月11日，上面呢班囡囡追EXO 登機。<br />\n<br />\n下面就大班黑衫巿民叫口號。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFYp30a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFYp30a.jpg&h=562e3bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kgZwJZ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkgZwJZ6.jpg&h=c9c82f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bdUD8rO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbdUD8rO.jpg&h=61c2f13b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c3361faae21a41628d44086a85052ffc2b322cb","tid":1528196,"uid":206117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e967fb1a2c9ac21447352347d4a9095fe33f27","tid":1528196,"uid":197256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:32:29.000Z","msg":"推撚到"},{"pid":"59228cb18376c03e6573ab0484e55f63636f3534","tid":1528196,"uid":206117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:36:41.000Z","msg":"CLS粉絲"},{"pid":"e4be6b3734040ba6e9515d33494afe34aae5060d","tid":1528196,"uid":165711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"近支者赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b693a60f1e05caf1faffc99c5c6597b7b0f480ea","tid":1528196,"uid":206117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:40:19.000Z","msg":"咁樣阻住架飛機真係好仆街"},{"pid":"d1ebed17c34f8d2ea3c95c6fba3aced093fa16f7","tid":1528196,"uid":277455,"like"